snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry importAptArtifacts Sample
snippets.description: Imports Apt artifacts. The returned Operation will complete once the resources are imported. Package, Version, and File resources are created based on the imported artifacts. Imported artifacts that conflict with existing resources are ignored.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry importYumArtifacts Sample
snippets.description: Imports Yum (RPM) artifacts. The returned Operation will complete once the resources are imported. Package, Version, and File resources are created based on the imported artifacts. Imported artifacts that conflict with existing resources are ignored.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry createRepository Sample
snippets.description: Creates a repository. The returned Operation will finish once the repository has been created. Its response will be the created Repository.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry deleteRepository Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a repository and all of its contents. The returned Operation will finish once the repository has been deleted. It will not have any Operation metadata and will return a google.protobuf.Empty response.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry deletePackage Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a package and all of its versions and tags. The returned operation will complete once the package has been deleted.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry deleteVersion Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a version and all of its content. The returned operation will complete once the version has been deleted.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry batchDeleteVersions Sample
snippets.description: Deletes multiple versions across a repository. The returned operation will complete once the versions have been deleted.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry deleteFile Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a file and all of its content. It is only allowed on generic repositories. The returned operation will complete once the file has been deleted.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry setIamPolicy Sample
snippets.description: Updates the IAM policy for a given resource.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry getIamPolicy Sample
snippets.description: Gets the IAM policy for a given resource.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry testIamPermissions Sample
snippets.description: Tests if the caller has a list of permissions on a resource.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry getProjectSettings Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves the Settings for the Project.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry updateProjectSettings Sample
snippets.description: Updates the Settings for the Project.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry getVPCSCConfig Sample
snippets.description: Retrieves the VPCSC Config for the Project.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry updateVPCSCConfig Sample
snippets.description: Updates the VPCSC Config for the Project.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry createAttachment Sample
snippets.description: Creates an attachment. The returned Operation will finish once the attachment has been created. Its response will be the created attachment.

snippets.title: ArtifactRegistry deleteAttachment Sample
snippets.description: Deletes an attachment. The returned Operation will finish once the attachments has been deleted. It will not have any Operation metadata and will return a `google.protobuf.Empty` response.
